I"³<h3 id="the-hottest-neighborhood-frozen-in-time">The hottest neighborhood frozen in <strong>time</strong>.</h3>

<p>Munrae-dong is one of the rising hipster hot places in Seoul for young local. Munrae-dong was a representative metal industry in Seoul. But over time, the ironworks went out of business and people stopped coming to the area. The government started Munrae-art-factory for support for young artists, and the artists started their workrooms in empty places in the area. The area became called â€˜Munrae Creative villageâ€™. As remaining ironworks and artist village harmonize together, Munrae-dong has quaint atmosphere. Many young people are charmed by the atmosphere where there is the juxtapoisition of old and new, past and present. I also periodically visit Munrae-dong. At the last part of posting, Iâ€™ll let you know my favorite place in Munrae-dong.</p>

