<p>Some artists whose workspace is in Munrae painted a mural so that the normal buildings became individual ones.</p>

<p><strong><em>Tips</em></strong>  Â  Munrae-dong is close to Hongdae (it takes 20 minutes by car), so youâ€™d better go to both areas a day. For example, you can spend your leisure time in Munrae-dong by day and have a exciting time at clubs in Hongdae by night.</p>

<p><strong><em>Way to go</em></strong> Â  2 minutes walk from Exit 7 of Munrae Station (Subway line 2)</p>

